The paper deals with content-based video indexing and retrieval, which involves multimedia analysis, information retrieval, computer vision, natural language processing, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.MM (Multimedia), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
